WEBVTT

00:02.400 --> 00:05.665
If you do not challenge the corrupt,
then commoners will rise.

00:05.840 --> 00:07.387
Truro lacks an MP.

00:07.560 --> 00:10.984
Sir Francis intends to put up his own candidate
to challenge Falmouth's.

00:11.160 --> 00:12.422
I regret I must decline.

00:12.600 --> 00:13.669
