16:29.880 --> 16:33.464
My Lord de Dunstanville, is life much altered
by your elevation to the peerage?

16:33.640 --> 16:37.269
Oh, not in the least. My dogs are as lazy
and my daughter as wilful.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.702
(Laughter)

16:38.880 --> 16:41.257
