(Silence)

21:28.280 --> 21:31.226
There was a riot today on Truro quay.

21:31.600 --> 21:34.160
Charges relating to it are as follows:

21:34.920 --> 21:37.502
theft, violent affray,

21:37.680 --> 21:39.705
common assault,

