to make it so.

33:19.880 --> 33:23.782
From Hugh. Will I attend on him
at Tregothnan tomorrow?

33:25.200 --> 33:26.781
Is he unwell?

33:26.960 --> 33:30.737
He says he wants to reassure his uncle
that he's fit to stand for Parliament...

33:33.320 --> 33:36.869
