and you and Ross to join me.

33:37.880 --> 33:39.859
Oh.

33:50.840 --> 33:53.866
- (Water dripping)
- Will he bring Sister, do 'ee think?

33:58.120 --> 34:00.259
For her sake, let him not.

34:10.600 --> 34:13.387
Mistress be back. She be indoors.

34:14.000 --> 34:15.979
Does she suspect?

34:17.280 --> 34:19.544
- (She sobs)
- (He sighs)

34:28.320 --> 34:30.299
Ross...

34:31.120 --> 34:32.826
What happened in court?

34:33.640 --> 34:35.619
Some were treated fairly,

34:36.520 --> 34:38.499
others harshly.

34:39.760 --> 34:41.341
What's in the letter?

34:41.520 --> 34:43.499
It's from Hugh.

34:46.320 --> 34:48.538
Inviting us to Tregothnan tomorrow.

34:49.200 --> 34:51.179
Along with Dwight and Caroline.

34:58.880 --> 35:03.101
His letter speaks of a fever.
Of headaches and the like.

35:03.280 --> 35:06.864
I think... I think it would be
a kindness to visit.

35:10.120 --> 35:12.099
A kindness, yes.

35:15.480 --> 35:19.587
Do you think there's room...
in a woman's heart for two men?

35:22.440 --> 35:24.419
Or two women in a man's?

35:33.080 --> 35:35.059
No husband minds his wife...

35:36.120 --> 35:39.419
...being the one that other men desire but...

35:43.520 --> 35:46.580
...no man wants his wife to be
the one that other men possess.

35:47.800 --> 35:49.665
No, Ross.

35:53.000 --> 35:57.778
So, tomorrow, I have further business
regarding the arrests in Truro.

35:58.360 --> 36:00.339
But you...

36:04.280 --> 36:06.419
You go to Tregothnan.

36:07.400 --> 36:09.379
If you think I should.

36:12.160 --> 36:14.139
I do.

