(Shouting from crowd)

44:17.800 --> 44:19.119
(Angry shouting)

44:22.760 --> 44:24.421
Have mercy.

44:32.040 --> 44:33.541
(Pleading for mercy)

45:09.560 --> 45:11.983
One moment! One moment!

45:20.120 --> 45:21.940
My Lords...

45:24.600 --> 45:27.023
...when we send a man to meet his Maker,

45:27.720 --> 45:31.781
we must be very certain...
not only of his guilt,

45:31.960 --> 45:35.657
but of our motives in doing so.

45:36.840 --> 45:39.707
Is our aim to see justice done...

45:40.520 --> 45:43.978
- ...or is it to terrify people into submission?
- This man has no authority here.

45:44.160 --> 45:46.139
- He has no right...
- Let him speak.

45:47.120 --> 45:48.508
My Lords, I admit

45:48.680 --> 45:52.377
these are difficult times
to be merciful.

45:52.560 --> 45:56.189
When authority is challenged,
our impulse is to reassert it

45:56.360 --> 45:58.339
in the sternest way possible.

45:59.200 --> 46:02.784
But consider,
here we face conditions

46:02.960 --> 46:05.224
harsher than we have ever known.

46:05.800 --> 46:07.779
Grain is shipped abroad...

46:08.760 --> 46:10.739
...while ordinary people starve.

46:13.640 --> 46:17.098
These men have no grievance
against authority...

46:20.000 --> 46:23.697
...but against the merchants
who grow fat on trade while people die.

46:23.880 --> 46:25.541
(People call out in agreement)

46:30.080 --> 46:33.584
To show mercy now
would not be a sign of weakness.

46:35.280 --> 46:37.259
A signal that justice...

46:38.560 --> 46:42.940
...real justice, had been served...
would be a reprieve.

46:48.560 --> 46:50.027
- Reprieve!
- Reprieve!

46:50.200 --> 46:53.340
OTHERS: Reprieve! Reprieve!

46:54.600 --> 46:56.784
CROWD: Reprieve! Reprieve! Reprieve!

47:03.160 --> 47:05.139
So Ross could not come.

47:06.600 --> 47:08.261
He had business in town.

47:12.760 --> 47:15.467
I think 'tis better if we do not meet at all now.

47:17.200 --> 47:19.339
Do I disquiet you so?

47:19.520 --> 47:21.499
I think we disquiet each other.

47:27.720 --> 47:29.699
Demelza, I must tell you...

47:30.360 --> 47:33.705
